## Create a new result

### Request attributes

Attribute           | Required | Description
--------------------|----------|------------
status              | Yes      | Partner result status. Must be __"sending"__, __"sent"__, __"pending"__, __"completed"__ or __"failed"__.
candidate-id        | Yes      | Numeric identifier for the candidate.
summary             | Optional | Summary text shown on the candidate profile.
job-id              | Optional | ID of the job webhook was sent from.
url                 | Optional | URL for viewing a report on your website. Must be a valid HTTP or HTTPS URL.
assessment          | Optional | Assessment object. `score` must be between 0 and 100, `grade` may be __"top_fit"__, __"might_be_fit"__, __"might_not_be_fit"__, __"unknown"__ or __null__, and `duration` accepts seconds or `HH:MM:SS`.
details             | Optional | Details object displayed to the customer. Must be valid JSON with a maximum depth of 2.
attachments         | Optional | List of attachment objects containing exactly __"url"__ and __"description"__.
actions             | Optional | List of action objects containing `buttonText` and `endpoint`.
assessment-criteria | Optional | List of assessment criteria objects containing `id` and optional `score` between 0 and 100.

```http
POST https://api.teamtailor.com/partner/v1/partner-results HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer abc123abc123
X-Api-Version: <%= config[:api_version] %>
Content-Type: application/vnd.api+json

{
  "data":{
    "type": "partner-results",
    "attributes":{
      "status": "completed",
      "summary": "The candidate passed the test with excellent results",
      "job-id": 444,
      "candidate-id": 102,
      "assessment": {
        "score": 82,
        "grade": "top_fit",
        "duration": "0:32:14"
      },
      "details": {
        "rating": "10",
        "awesomeness": "confirmed"
      }
    }
  }
}
```
